Q: 请提供注册号为n829dl的飞机在2024年每个月的飞行量是多少？按月份排序。
SQL:
SELECT
        date_month,
        count(*) AS num
FROM
        zts_plane_flight_1
WHERE
        pure_reg COLLATE utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci= "n829dl" COLLATE utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci
        AND date_month BETWEEN '2024-01'
        AND '2024-12'
GROUP BY
        date_month
ORDER BY
        date_month ASC;
